{"tid":652570,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［00後］仲有冇人識《住屋村大》？","createTime":"2018-05-04T02:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T07:05:00.000Z","uid":10925,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d19390a0c1d585f523bd9e648e5be4747b70cd7","tid":652570,"uid":10925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見隔離post 有醫神同古仔討論，<br />\n就諗起當年《勁歌金曲》真係好神。<br />\n果個年代邊忽有歌係10分鐘。<br />\n仲要首首神曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《住屋村大》班友其實都算好叻。<br />\n首首神曲都都比佢地改過哂。<br />\n實在算係當年網絡創作一大成就。<br />\n<br />\n反觀現在，原曲又冇咩經典作，改歌又冇咩叻仔。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時代唔同Lu. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71238934ca2c2babdaa54b81a6007ec2a60a648","tid":652570,"uid":10925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:55:17.000Z","msg":"一定係引哂00後入黎，之後真係唔知我up乜，上一頁"},{"pid":"15d6f57ddcd17e24bd8476c97f592bae34f019c9","tid":652570,"uid":51895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:58:39.000Z","msg":"細個 訓公屋四十座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060e3f55658175d66e02eea069d4ab00887a94ca","tid":652570,"uid":52930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15d6f57ddcd17e24bd8476c97f592bae34f019c9","tid":652570,"uid":51895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:58:39.000Z","msg":"細個 訓公屋四十座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:59:29.000Z","msg":"住係對面肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4b46653c7c2a75ed9174c206ca2f33b8a0f80d","tid":652570,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T03:03:54.000Z","msg":"我自細就有便